9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:45,780
=Episode 29=

16
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:48,840
(Dongchao,)

17
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,599
(are you ready for your speech)

18
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:53,200
(at the financing conference tomorrow?)

19
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,159
(We've planned this for so long.)

20
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,760
(We can't afford any mistakes.)

21
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,200
(Don't forget)

22
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,719
(the determination you had)

23
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:05,280
(when you left the US)

24
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,599
(to join Lysen Group.)

25
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:14,820
(Ten years ago. New York, USA)

26
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,919
You'll be fine.

27
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,599
Dry heat upon my brow?

28
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,840
Oh! Time was,

29
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:22,199
when as the sunrise nobly spurred me,

30
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,919
so the sunset soothed.

31
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,840
No more.

32
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,439
This lovely light,

33
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,840
it lights not me.

34
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:33,840
All loveliness is anguish to me,

35
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:36,719
since I can ne'er enjoy.

36
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:39,919
Gifted with the high perception,

37
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:43,639
I lack the low, enjoying power.

38
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,439
Darn it.

39
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:51,280
Most subtly and most malignantly!

40
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:56,680
Darn it. In the midst of Paradise!

41
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,680
Goodnight.

42
00:04:37,199 --> 00:04:38,519
Goodnight.

43
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:42,800
I really think you should move her
to another clinic.

44
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:44,399
I heard Houston has

45
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:46,680
