52
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,879
and new technologies.

53
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:21,000
But the possibility of that working
is really low, isn't it?

54
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:29,600
Chao, just pray to God.

55
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,079
She's a good person.

56
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,800
We all should believe in miracles.

57
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:35,879
Miracles?

58
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:39,519
Miracles?

59
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,360
Good people

60
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:54,240
