84
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,519
I was the one who rushed him back.

85
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:14,319
He didn't even go back
when his wife died.

86
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:15,600
He's that determined.

87
00:07:15,759 --> 00:07:16,800
If I give up now,

88
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,199
I'll never have another chance.

89
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:21,000
Dad, I believe in Mr. Jiang.

90
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,240
Don't forget,

91
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:25,720
