103
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:52,839
Give Mr. Jiang a chance.

104
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:54,560
Give me a chance too, please.

105
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,399
Dad.

106
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:04,319
