110
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,120
Nice shot.

111
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,559
Good putt.

112
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:43,759
How you play the rest

113
00:08:45,519 --> 00:08:46,559
