116
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,519
Dad, let me walk you out.

117
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,039
Hello?

118
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:04,799
Hello, Chao.

119
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:09,919
