130
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,799
Thank you, Doctor.

131
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:48,440
Goodnight.

132
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:07,440
In chess...

133
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:12,919
The Generals never meet.

134
