140
00:10:30,639 --> 00:10:37,100
(Marshal)

141
00:10:39,220 --> 00:10:39,980
(Lysen Group Financing Conference)

142
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:59,020
(Lysen Group Financing Conference)

143
