00:32:30,279 --> 00:32:31,880
I'm completely powerless.

578
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:34,759
Ms. Wan, don't be afraid.

579
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:38,440
We just hope

580
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,039
you can help us find

581
00:32:41,039 --> 00:32:42,200
the evidence we need

582
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,200
of his financial crimes.

583
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,240
So, Little Genius,

584
00:32:47,359 --> 00:32:48,599
what's the plan from here?

585
00:32:51,799 --> 00:32:52,599
Next,

586
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:57,240
I'm going to expose his scheme.

587
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:58,200
Mr. Jiang.

588
00:33:00,119 --> 00:33:00,960
It's been a while.

589
00:33:09,799 --> 00:33:11,039
I didn't realize that

590
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:13,350
on top of your brilliant
stand-up performances,

591
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,519
you could stay so composed

592
00:33:15,519 --> 00:33:16,599
in such pressure.

593
00:33:24,200 --> 00:33:26,440
I'm Yu Peidong,

594
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:29,039
formerly worked at Investment Dept 3.

595
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:31,119
Beside me

596
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:34,880
is the current HR Director
of Lysen Group, Ren Jing,

597
00:33:36,039 --> 00:33:37,920
along with our former colleagues

598
00:33:38,119 --> 00:33:38,920
from Dept 3.

599
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:43,759
At the request of Mr. Li Wancheng
and Ms. Rao Yuci,

600
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:46,519
we've conducted a secret review

601
00:33:46,519 --> 00:33:48,319
of every investment case handled
by Jiang Dongchao

602
00:33:48,319 --> 00:33:49,759
during his decade at Lysen Group.

603
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,119
That includes several

604
00:33:51,119 --> 00:33:52,240
of the famous success stories

605
00:33:52,240 --> 00:33:53,279
you're all familiar with.

606
00:33:55,799 --> 00:33:56,640
But among these,

607
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:57,440
there are dozens

608
00:33:57,440 --> 00:33:59,319
of overseas investment projects

609
00:33:59,319 --> 00:34:00,740
(List of Jiang Dongchao's
Overseas Investment)

610
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:03,160
with massive red flags.

611
00:34:03,839 --> 00:34:05,039
Owners fleeing,

612
00:34:05,960 --> 00:34:06,759
bankruptcies,

613
00:34:07,519 --> 00:34:08,880
major clients vanishing,

614
00:34:09,239 --> 00:34:11,400
and collapses due to mismanagement.

615
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:12,920
Looking at the fate

616
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:14,480
of these acquired companies,

617
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:15,400
it's clear

618
00:34:15,679 --> 00:34:17,440
how our very own Mr. Jiang Dongchao

619
00:34:17,599 --> 00:34:19,719
used these mergers

620
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:21,400
to line his own pockets.

621
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:26,020
(Jiang Dongchao's Overseas Investment)

622
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:27,880
Every single one of these

623
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:29,079
overseas investments

624
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:31,280
and acquisitions failed
without exception.

625
00:34:31,599 --> 00:34:33,119
(Capital Operation)
As for the funneled funds,

626
00:34:33,519 --> 00:34:34,760
through a series

627
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:36,800
of maneuvers by Mr. Jiang Dongchao,

628
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:38,880
they flowed into an offshore trust.

629
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,679
Qingyu,

630
00:34:41,880 --> 00:34:43,280
you're on your own now.

631
00:35:01,559 --> 00:35:03,000
As for the beneficiary

632
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:03,760
of that trust...

633
00:35:09,960 --> 00:35:11,000
It's your daughter,

634
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:12,760
Chloe.

635
00:35:20,480 --> 00:35:21,960
I don't want Chloe

636
00:35:22,119 --> 00:35:23,920
to be hurt the way I was.

637
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:27,559
Jiang Dongchao has hurt
everyone in this room.

638
00:35:28,719 --> 00:35:29,519
Ms. Dai,

639
00:35:30,159 --> 00:35:31,239
he heartlessly abandoned you

640
00:35:31,239 --> 00:35:32,559
when you were gravely ill.

641
00:35:34,199 --> 00:35:35,000
Ms. Xin,

642
00:35:35,679 --> 00:35:37,559
(he backstabbed your husband,
Xian Donghai,)

643
00:35:37,890 --> 00:35:39,760
(causing Yuanjian Capital
to lose the gamble.)

644
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:41,599
Ms. Wan,

645
00:35:42,200 --> 00:35:43,440
(he used both physical violence)

646
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:45,280
(and psychological control on you.)

647
00:35:48,599 --> 00:35:49,400
Mr. Pengyu,

648
00:35:50,679 --> 00:35:53,239
(you lost the father who loved you
because of him.)

649
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:01,559
This financing conference

650
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,280
is the perfect chance

651
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:05,079
to expose his crimes to the world.

652
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:07,760
I need everyone to work with me

653
00:36:08,679 --> 00:36:10,199
to make sure he faces justice.

654
00:36:13,239 --> 00:36:15,119
(Dismissal of Jiang Dongchao as CEO)
This is your dismissal notice.

655
00:36:16,039 --> 00:36:16,639
It carries

656
00:36:16,639 --> 00:36:18,599
the signatures of all the board members.

657
00:36:44,660 --> 00:36:48,220
=Episode 29=
(The Defeated)

658
00:36:48,741 --> 00:36:51,181
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

659
00:36:51,181 --> 00:36:57,381
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

660
00:36:58,141 --> 00:37:01,341
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

661
00:37:01,341 --> 00:37:05,861
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

662
00:37:05,861 --> 00:37:13,381
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

663
00:37:13,381 --> 00:37:17,301
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

664
00:37:17,301 --> 00:37:21,341
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

665
00:37:21,341 --> 00:37:24,861
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

666
00:37:24,861 --> 00:37:28,821
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

667
00:37:28,821 --> 00:37:32,981
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

668
00:37:32,981 --> 00:37:37,181
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

669
00:37:37,181 --> 00:37:40,981
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

670
00:37:40,981 --> 00:37:45,061
♪Keep walking through the light♪

671
00:37:45,061 --> 00:37:49,261
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

672
00:37:49,261 --> 00:37:55,581
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

673
00:38:12,701 --> 00:38:19,341
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

674
00:38:19,341 --> 00:38:23,181
♪An apology that came too late♪

675
00:38:23,181 --> 00:38:27,821
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

676
00:38:27,901 --> 00:38:35,301
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

677
00:38:35,301 --> 00:38:39,381
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

678
00:38:39,381 --> 00:38:43,461
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

679
00:38:43,461 --> 00:38:47,461
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

680
00:38:47,461 --> 00:38:51,221
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

681
00:38:51,221 --> 00:38:55,421
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

682
00:38:55,421 --> 00:38:59,581
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

683
00:38:59,581 --> 00:39:03,301
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

684
00:39:03,301 --> 00:39:07,341
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

685
00:39:07,341 --> 00:39:11,381
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

686
00:39:11,381 --> 00:39:17,581
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
